Uses of Package
com.mhealthatlas.enterprisemanagement.dto

Packages that use com.mhealthatlas.enterprisemanagement.dto 
Package Description
com.mhealthatlas.enterprisemanagement.command
com.mhealthatlas.enterprisemanagement.command is a group of services which only mutate data but have not advanced query functionalities.
com.mhealthatlas.enterprisemanagement.controller
com.mhealthatlas.enterprisemanagement.controller is a group of REST API controllers in the enterprise management service.
Each class ending with the QueryController prefix provides GET API endpoints for quering information.
Each class ending with the CommandController prefix provides POST and DELETE API endpoints for mutating the information state.
com.mhealthatlas.enterprisemanagement.dto
com.mhealthatlas.enterprisemanagement.dto contains all data transfer object definitions.
com.mhealthatlas.enterprisemanagement.query
com.mhealthatlas.enterprisemanagement.query is a group of services which only queries data but does not mutate them.
com.mhealthatlas.enterprisemanagement.services
com.mhealthatlas.enterprisemanagement.services contains all service which interact with external resources.
